CHANNEL SWIMMER
A daughter, a sister a wife, a friend.
Susan sends this message to you.
Sit awhile, contemplate the challenge ahead!
Arise, and take up that challenge!
Swin strong, swim straight, swim true!
Swim with me! Swim with my spirit!
Achieve your goal!
And bring me back a French pebble
Enjoy your journey and have faith in yourself"Ģ
